<li>Ruben D Cohen (2006) "A VaR-Based Model for the Yield Curve <a href="http://rdcohen.50megs.com/YieldCurveabstract.htm" class="external text" title="http://rdcohen.50megs.com/YieldCurveabstract.htm" rel="nofollow">[download</a>]" <i>Wilmott Magazine</i>, May Issue.</li>
<li>Paul F. Cwik (2005) "The Inverted Yield Curve and the Economic Downturn <a href="http://pcpe.libinst.cz/nppe/1_1/nppe1_1_1.pdf" class="external text" title="http://pcpe.libinst.cz/nppe/1_1/nppe1_1_1.pdf" rel="nofollow">[download</a>]" <i><a href="/wiki/New_Perspectives_on_Political_Economy" title="New Perspectives on Political Economy">New Perspectives on Political Economy</a></i>, Volume 1, Number 1, 2005, pp. 1-37.</li>
<li>Roger Wets, Stephen Bianchi &amp; Liming Yang (2002), "Serious Zero-Curves" <a href="http://www.math.ucdavis.edu/~rjbw/ARTICLES/zcrv.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.math.ucdavis.edu/~rjbw/ARTICLES/zcrv.pdf" rel="nofollow">[download</a>]"</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Yield_curve&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ecb.int/stats/money/yc/html/index.en.html/" class="external text" title="http://www.ecb.int/stats/money/yc/html/index.en.html/" rel="nofollow">Euro area yield curves</a> - European Central Bank website</li>
<li><a href="http://stockcharts.com/charts/YieldCurve.html" class="external text" title="http://stockcharts.com/charts/YieldCurve.html" rel="nofollow">Dynamic Yield Curve</a> - This chart shows the relationship between interest rates and stocks over time.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bramaan.com" class="external text" title="http://www.bramaan.com" rel="nofollow">Bramaan.com</a> - A free online utility to bootstrap LIBOR yield curves.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.bba.org.uk/bba/jsp/polopoly.jsp?d=141&amp;a=627" class="external text" title="http://www.bba.org.uk/bba/jsp/polopoly.jsp?d=141&amp;a=627" rel="nofollow">British Banker's Association page with historic yield curve data in various currencies</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.newyorkfed.org/research/current_issues/ci2-7.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.newyorkfed.org/research/current_issues/ci2-7.pdf" rel="nofollow">NYFed Current Issue</a> - Current Issue of New York Federal Reserve outlining their view of inverted yield curve</li>
</ul>
